---
import ToolLayout from "../layouts/ToolLayout.astro";

const title = "Privacy Policy";
const description =
  "Easy2GoHub Privacy Policy: local processing (no uploads by default), cookies, analytics, and Google AdSense advertising.";
const canonical = "https://www.easy2gohub.com/privacy-policy/";
---

<ToolLayout title={title} description={description} canonical={canonical} adsProfile="none">
  <section class="tool-card p-10 space-y-6">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-slate-900 text-center">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      This Privacy Policy explains how Easy2GoHub (“we”, “our”, “us”) handles information when you use our website and
      browser-based tools. Easy2GoHub focuses on privacy-first utilities that run locally in your browser.
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">1) Local Processing (No Uploads by Default)</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
        Most Easy2GoHub tools process your files locally in your browser. For our current image tools, the images you add
        are processed on your device and are not uploaded to our servers by default.
      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
        If we introduce any feature that requires uploading files to a server in the future, we will clearly disclose that
        on the tool page before you use it.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">2) Information We Collect</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
        We may collect limited information to operate and improve the website:
      </p>
      <ul class="mt-2 space-y-2 text-slate-700 leading-relaxed list-disc pl-6">
        <li>
          <span class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Basic usage and log data:</span> pages visited, approximate region,
          device/browser type, and performance metrics.
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Cookies and similar technologies:</span> used for site preferences,
          analytics, and advertising (see below).
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
        We do not intentionally collect sensitive personal information through our tools. Do not submit sensitive personal
        data to the site.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">3) Cookies</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
        Cookies are small files stored by your browser. We and our partners may use cookies (or similar technologies) to:
      </p>
      <ul class="mt-2 space-y-2 text-slate-700 leading-relaxed list-disc pl-6">
        <li>remember preferences and improve user experience</li>
        <li>measure site performance and understand aggregated usage</li>
        <li>deliver and measure ads (if ads are enabled)</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
        You can control cookies through your browser settings. Disabling cookies may affect some site functionality.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">4) Google AdSense (Advertising)</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
        We may display ads served by Google AdSense. Google and its partners may use cookies to serve ads based on your
        visits to this and other websites. Depending on your settings, this may include personalized advertising.
      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
        You can manage or opt out of personalized ads in Google’s Ads Settings, and learn more about how Google uses
        information in Google’s privacy and advertising resources.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">5) Data Security</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
        We take reasonable steps to protect the website. However, no method of transmission over the internet or method of
        electronic storage is 100% secure.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">6) Children’s Privacy</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
        Easy2GoHub is not directed to children under 13, and we do not knowingly collect personal information from children.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">7) Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
        We may update this policy from time to time. The most recent version will be posted on this page.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">8) Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
        If you have questions about this policy, contact us at:
        <span class="font-semibold text-slate-900"> easy2gohub@gmail.com</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</ToolLayout>